# Day-3: Blog Title Kaise Likhe Jo Log Padhein

Today I learned 3 tricks for writing blog titles:

1. Number Use Karo = "5 Tips" ya "3 Galtiyan" log click karte hain
2. Problem + Solution = "C Nahi Aati? Ye 1 Trick Try Karo" 
3. Curiosity Banao = "Main Fail Hui Par Phir Bhi Internship Mili"

Best line I learned: "Title is like shop ka board. Achha hoga to log aayenge."
